[
  {
    "text": "日常生活的织锦",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.10071910091700689,
      "left": 0.3627450829248366,
      "width": 0.27450980620914983,
      "height": 0.030303029040404043
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "早晨的阳光照亮了安静的街道,温暖的光",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.16446939418877496,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "线穿过树叶,在地面上投下斑驳的影子。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "鸟儿在树上轻声歌唱,它们的歌声欢快而",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2099239377493811,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "清",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2326512095296841,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.01960784330065356,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "脆,唤醒了沉睡的城市,开始新的一天",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2326512095296841,
      "left": 0.13725489722222217,
      "width": 0.33333333611111055,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "充满",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2553784813099871,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.03921568660130712,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "希望和可能性。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2553784813099871,
      "left": 0.15686274052287574,
      "width": 0.13725490310457494,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科技的发展正在以前所未有的速度改变我",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29041635863795434,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "们的生活方式和工作模式。每天都有新的",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3131436304182573,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "创新和发明出现,从人工智能到可再生能",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3358709021985603,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "源,这些技术进步深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35859817397886334,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.17647058970588206,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻地影响着社会的方",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35859817397886334,
      "left": 0.29411764362745074,
      "width": 0.17647058970588198,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "方面面,重塑着我们与世界互动",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3813254457591663,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.27450980620914983,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的方式。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3813254457591663,
      "left": 0.3921568601307185,
      "width": 0.0784313732026142,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "古代文明建造了令人惊叹的纪念碑和建筑",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4173102927446461,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "奇迹,这些宏伟的结构历经千年依然屹立",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4400375645249492,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "不倒。从埃及的金字塔到中国的长城,这",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.46276483630525217,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "些建筑不仅展示了我们祖先的非凡智慧和",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.48549210808555515,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "惊人的创造力,也见证了人类文明的辉煌",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5082193798658583,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "历程。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5309466516461613,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.058823529901960686,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "教育是",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5659845289741284,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.058823529901960686,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "推",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5659845289741284,
      "left": 0.17647058382352931,
      "width": 0.01960784330065356,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "动社会进步和个人发展的根本基",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5659845289741284,
      "left": 0.19607842712418289,
      "width": 0.27450980620914983,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "础。通过系统",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5887118007544315,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1176470598039214,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的学习和持续的知识积累,",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5887118007544315,
      "left": 0.23529411372549,
      "width": 0.2352941196078427,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "人们能够获得改",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6114390725347345,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1372549031045749,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "善",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6114390725347345,
      "left": 0.2549019570261436,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "自己生活和周围社区所",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6114390725347345,
      "left": 0.2745098003267971,
      "width": 0.19607843300653557,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "需",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6341663443150376,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.01960784330065356,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的各种工具、技能和深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6341663443150376,
      "left": 0.13725489722222217,
      "width": 0.19607843300653557,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻见解,从而为",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6341663443150376,
      "left": 0.33333333022875783,
      "width": 0.13725490310457486,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "建设更美好",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6568936160953404,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.09803921650326781,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的未来做出贡献。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6568936160953404,
      "left": 0.21568627042483643,
      "width": 0.1568627464052285,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "大自然慷慨地提供了无与伦比的美丽景观",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.6919314934233078,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "和维持生命所必",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7146587652036108,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.1372549031045749,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "需",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7146587652036108,
      "left": 0.2549019570261436,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的各种宝贵资源。从清",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7146587652036108,
      "left": 0.2745098003267971,
      "width": 0.19607843300653557,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "新的空气到纯净的水源,从肥沃的土壤到",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7373860369839138,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "多样",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7601133087642169,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.03921568660130712,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "的生物。保",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7601133087642169,
      "left": 0.15686274052287574,
      "width": 0.09803921650326776,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "护",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7601133087642169,
      "left": 0.2549019570261436,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "和珍惜环",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7601133087642169,
      "left": 0.2745098003267971,
      "width": 0.07843137320261424,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "境",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7601133087642169,
      "left": 0.3529411735294114,
      "width": 0.01960784330065354,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "不仅是我们",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7601133087642169,
      "left": 0.37254901683006497,
      "width": 0.09803921650326775,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "这一代人的责任,更是确",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7828405805445199,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.2156862763071892,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "保后代子孙能够",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.7828405805445199,
      "left": 0.33333333022875783,
      "width": 0.13725490310457486,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "继续享受地球奇观的关键。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.805567852324823,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.23529411960784274,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "有效的交流在不同文化、民族和国家之间",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8415526993103027,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.35294117941176406,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "架",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.8642799710906058,
      "left": 0.11764705392156861,
      "width": 0.01960784330065356,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "起了理解与合作的重要桥梁。语言作为",
