      "height": 0.011363635890151517
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "人类最伟大的发明之一,使我们能够跨越",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.16446939418877496,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "地理和文化的界限,分享彼",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.23529411960784238,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "此的想法、经",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.1871966659690781,
      "left": 0.7549019410947705,
      "width": 0.11764705980392104,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "验和智慧,从而建立起相互理解、尊重和",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2099239377493811,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "信任的关系。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2326512095296841,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.11764705980392133,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "科学研究通过严谨的方法和不懈的探索,",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.2676890868576512,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "正在逐步揭示宇宙中",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29041635863795434,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.17647058970588195,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "那些深藏的奥秘和规",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.29041635863795434,
      "left": 0.69607841119281,
      "width": 0.17647058970588148,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "律。每一个新的发现都像是打开了一扇通",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3131436304182573,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "往未知世界的大门,同时也带来了更多令",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3358709021985603,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.01515151452020195
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "人着迷的问题,激励着科学家们继续前",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.35859817397886334,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.33333333611111027,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "行,探索更广阔的未知领域。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.3813254457591663,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.2549019629084959,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "艺术以其独特的方式表达和传递那些超越",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4173102927446461,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117636,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "语言文字限制的深",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4400375645249492,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.1568627464052284,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "刻情感和抽象思想。无",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.4400375645249492,
      "left": 0.6764705678921564,
      "width": 0.1960784330065351,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "论是绘画、音乐、雕塑还是文学,这些富",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.46276483630525217,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "有创意的艺术作品不仅能够激发人们的想",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.48549210808555515,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "象力和创造力,还能挑战我们既有的观",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5082193798658583,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.33333333611111005,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "念,引导我们从全新的角度来审视和理解",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5309466516461613,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.3529411794117634,
      "height": 0.015151514520202022
    },
    "normalized_conf": 1,
    "engine": "pdftext"
  },
  {
    "text": "这个复杂多彩的世界。",
    "bounds": {
      "top": 0.5536739234264643,
      "left": 0.5196078214869281,
      "width": 0.1960784330065355,
